          p You need to create a company in order to continue
      hr
      footer.clearfix
        a href="companies/new" class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'
          .fa.fa-plus
          | Add New Company

  .col-md-4.col-sm-4.mb ng-repeat="company in companies"
